<A>__{the 737 lands.}
<L>__{exterior superhub night minutes later}
<A>__{one of a seemingly endless line of fedex planes, our 737 taxis to a gate at the fedex superhub. the hub is a vast living organism loud, complex, overwhelming, as much a symbol of modern life as was the factory in modern times. five thousand people work in a frenzy of interconnected activity inside three vast hangers brightly lit. hundreds of forklifts and cargo pullers dart about, their headlights crisscrossing like a laser show. loaders quickly roll the container onto a forklift.}
